19:42.100 --> 19:44.100 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

19:44.100 --> 19:46.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KENNETH DAVIS, President
and CEO, Mount Sinai
Health System: Absolutely.

19:46.200 --> 19:48.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think, if anything, there are
