19:48.733 --> 19:53.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Particularly, the glide path
to per capita or block grants
is going to produce a lower

19:55.633 --> 19:58.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
reimbursement for the states
