19:58.633 --> 20:01.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: What about
the effect on hospitals?

20:01.000 --> 20:03.000 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

20:03.000 --> 20:05.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KENNETH DAVIS: Well, there
are a number of things
