some of these costs down?

21:24.966 --> 21:26.533 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

21:26.533 --> 21:28.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
KENNETH DAVIS: Well,
let's remember all
hospitals are not alike.

21:28.166 --> 21:32.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
