how much Medicaid reimbursement

21:43.733 --> 21:46.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
or Medicare
reimbursement we get.

21:46.500 --> 21:51.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Additionally, as some systems
have increased in size, they
have done so in order that they

21:53.100 --> 21:56.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
