22:19.566 --> 22:24.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And in New York state, we
have seen 30-plus hospitals
go bankrupt in recent years.

22:24.200 --> 22:25.633 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So the lesson is?

22:25.633 --> 22:27.133 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

22:27.133 --> 22:28.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
KENNETH DAVIS: The lesson is,
we are focused on expenses.

22:28.300 --> 22:30.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We have to be
fixated on expenses.

22:30.500 --> 22:34.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But what we really need to do
-- and we were trying to do
this previously -- and hopefully

22:34.033 --> 22:37.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
