same level of care that others

23:19.666 --> 23:21.633 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
do.

23:21.633 --> 23:25.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And they point to studies
showing that, even with the
expansion of Medicaid, that that

23:27.566 --> 23:29.366 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
care is not getting much better.

23:29.366 --> 23:30.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
How do you respond?

23:30.366 --> 23:32.333 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

23:32.333 --> 23:35.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KENNETH DAVIS: Well, those
studies or study doesn't
take a very long perspective.

23:35.933 --> 23:40.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
