in things like mortality
for quite some time.

23:40.600 --> 23:45.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
If you're lowering
people's hemoglobin A1c
or better controlling
their blood pressure,

23:47.633 --> 23:51.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
