before you see an extension of
a lifespan in those patients.

23:52.966 --> 23:56.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But what we did find,
what was reported was an
improvement in mental health.

23:57.633 --> 24:00.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And it seems like people
have forgotten that.

24:00.600 --> 24:05.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
