recipients, at the very least,
have mental health problems.

24:13.500 --> 24:17.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
To take that out of the equation
is very, very destructive.

24:17.700 --> 24:21.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And to think that we're not
having a positive influence --
because the only thing we really

24:21.766 --> 24:26.233 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
