we can measure short-term
is improvement in mental
health -- is a little

24:26.233 --> 24:28.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
demeaning to our psychiatrists.

24:28.300 --> 24:32.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Let me go back
to the mega-question about our
whole -- our health care system.

24:34.233 --> 24:37.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
