24:55.333 --> 24:56.333 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

24:56.333 --> 24:58.366 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
KENNETH DAVIS: Not really.

24:58.366 --> 25:01.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
