well and out of the hospital.

25:26.566 --> 25:29.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We would have more incentives
for readmission penalties.

25:29.633 --> 25:32.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We would have incentives
for shorter stay.

25:32.033 --> 25:37.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We would have more incentives to
bring care to a less expensive
place, like the ambulatory

25:37.500 --> 25:38.933 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
setting.

25:38.933 --> 25:41.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But those issues aren't
being addressed in this bill.

25:41.566 --> 25:44.566 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And your
