they're not promoting...

25:45.033 --> 25:47.066 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

25:47.066 --> 25:50.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KENNETH DAVIS: If they are
truly interested in changing
the cost structure, making it

25:50.633 --> 25:55.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
more efficient and less
expensive, they have
got to deal with reforms
that actually affect

25:56.233 --> 25:57.800 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
those metrics.

25:57.800 --> 25:59.233 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
And these don't.

