want to be blamed when it
goes the other direction.

40:43.000 --> 40:47.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Your investment
decisions over time have been
remarkably right much of the

40:50.933 --> 40:53.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
time, most of the time.

40:53.000 --> 40:57.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
