40:58.533 --> 41:00.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT: They should
be willing to bet on America.

41:00.700 --> 41:03.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They shouldn't listen to a lot
of jabbering about what the
market's going to do tomorrow

41:03.333 --> 41:05.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
or next week or next month,
because nobody knows.

41:05.800 --> 41:10.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They should just keep buying
and buying and buying a little
bit of America as they go

41:10.033 --> 41:11.533 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
along.

41:11.533 --> 41:13.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
