they will have a lot of money.

41:13.600 --> 41:15.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Berkshire
Hathaway has made a huge
investment in Wells Fargo.

41:15.433 --> 41:17.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WARREN BUFFETT: True.

41:17.500 --> 41:21.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And you
-- it came up at your
recent shareholders
meeting that Wells Fargo

41:22.366 --> 41:23.666 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
