41:23.666 --> 41:25.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
They engaged in some...

41:25.066 --> 41:26.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
WARREN BUFFETT:
Plenty of problems.

41:26.233 --> 41:28.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF:
Plenty of problems.

41:28.166 --> 41:30.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
