41:32.833 --> 41:34.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WARREN BUFFETT: Right.

41:34.900 --> 41:38.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The critics are
saying, yes, you called them
out, but Berkshire Hathaway

41:39.933 --> 41:42.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
still owns a big
chunk of Wells Fargo.

41:42.666 --> 41:43.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WARREN BUFFETT: Sure.

41:43.666 --> 41:45.233 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Sure.

41:45.233 --> 41:46.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And
they're saying, is
there a double standard?

41:46.500 --> 41:47.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
WARREN BUFFETT: It was
a terrible mistake.

41:47.466 --> 41:49.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They incentivized bad behavior.

41:49.566 --> 41:53.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Incentives work, but they
work -- you incentivize good
behavior or bad behavior.

41:53.600 --> 41:58.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then the problem,
big problem is -- and
sometimes will you -- you
can design an incentive

41:59.933 --> 42:01.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
system that is incentivizing
the wrong things.

42:01.533 --> 42:04.133 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You have got to end it, and
end it fast and decisive.

42:04.133 --> 42:06.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So, that's where they
made the big mistake.

42:06.200 --> 42:10.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Is there a clear
line in your mind when behavior
becomes just so unacceptable

42:12.266 --> 42:13.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
that you don't want
to have anything to
do with that company?

42:13.766 --> 42:16.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT: Well, it's
a very interesting question.

42:16.066 --> 42:20.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I wouldn't want to
manufacture cigarettes.

42:20.533 --> 42:25.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
