42:27.533 --> 42:29.000 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Yes.

42:29.000 --> 42:31.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So I don't have a problem
owning stock in that.

42:31.600 --> 42:34.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But I just wouldn't want to --
I wouldn't want to do it myself.

42:34.433 --> 42:38.333 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I basically think, if
anything is sufficiently
antisocial, society
should do something about

42:38.333 --> 42:39.333 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
