seen that's 100 percent pure.

42:44.800 --> 42:48.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In terms of what I will call
them out for, I will call
individuals out, but generally

42:48.733 --> 42:50.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
