42:55.500 --> 42:56.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WARREN BUFFETT: Right.

42:56.966 --> 42:59.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And you
have been vocal about that.

42:59.100 --> 43:02.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
