to do to replace Obamacare,
the Affordable Care Act.

43:48.600 --> 43:50.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WARREN BUFFETT: Yes.

43:50.733 --> 43:53.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Do you
