have been some problems with it.

43:55.833 --> 43:59.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
WARREN BUFFETT: I think
that's way outside of
my circle of competence.

43:59.566 --> 44:02.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
